        Tier 1.2 (audit 2026-06-10) - Marathon finish vocabulary +
        5 knob templates with finish variants.

        20 distinct finishes harvested from
        ~/marathon_crawler/marathon_products.json (Marathon homepage
        scrape, June 2026). The configurator can pick a narrower
        subset via attr_pull_finish in southbrook_estimating; the
        full vendor vocabulary lives here as Marathon publishes it.
